{"tid":807233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"越南雙賊爆回收場擸5公斤銅線　撞正阿Sir走唔甩","createTime":"2018-09-05T10:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T12:22:37.000Z","uid":167928,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f540e9c0dd678f74d980a8be15e51ad9f388a7ce","tid":807233,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"屯門分區特遣隊於昨日(2日)晚上11時許，在區內進行反爆竊行動期間，於震寰路一個回收場發現一名南亞裔男子形迹可疑，警員擬截查時疑人一度拔足逃走，但終被截獲。警員其後於回收場截獲另一名南亞裔男子，並在附近檢獲一個疑屬於兩人的孭袋，內有5公斤銅線，懷疑是從回收場偷來，調查後以涉嫌爆竊將兩人拘捕，帶署扣查。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">疑犯來自越南，俱是以免遣返聲請獲發「行街紙」留港人士。 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/185218_017d784a9e15b654dfdfc0eb73bd7884.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F185218_017d784a9e15b654dfdfc0eb73bd7884.png&h=cab0701b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/05/185219_82b305bce5f5a31bc89f3def41cabf8e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F185219_82b305bce5f5a31bc89f3def41cabf8e.png&h=1e082b70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d265a98ac7b220b115c7d6c05fe8acf770c861f1","tid":807233,"uid":167928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:53:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 不漏洞拉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fabeb145ce09615faa224fa7b6adb5ce66e4d4","tid":807233,"uid":132587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:54:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://gifimage.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/metal-slug-gif-9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgifimage.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fmetal-slug-gif-9.gif&h=bf14716a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4eefe41